article_title: Georgia falls from 38th to 40th among most healthy states
article_text:
Georgia now ranks among the 11 most unhealthy states in the nation

State’s high rate of uninsured and low high school graduation rate are cited

State officials are working on Medicaid waiver plan to cover more people

article_metadata.title: Georgia falls from 38th to 40th among most healthy states | Columbus Ledger-Enquirer

og.description: Georgia slipped from 38th to 40th this year on the list of America’s most healthy states, according to a ranking released Thursday by the United Health Foundation.
